# üì¶ STAGE 3 HANDOFF PACKAGE

**When executing as part of the pipeline**, after completing the presentation outline and process notes, output the following handoff package for Stage 4:

```markdown
<<<STAGE_3_HANDOFF>>>

## Pipeline Metadata
| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
